data.description: This beautiful one-story residence in Harker Heights offers the perfect blend of comfort, style, and functionality. As you step inside this 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home, you'll be greeted by an open and airy floor plan with abundant natural light. The separate office space, complete with French doors, offers a tranquil and productive environment for remote work or study. The two dining areas provide flexibility for both casual family meals and formal entertaining. One of the highlights of this property is the lush backyard oasis. The recent fence upgrade ensures privacy, creating the ideal setting for outdoor activities and relaxation. The concrete patio extension is the perfect spot for barbecues, al fresco dining, or simply enjoying your morning coffee in a serene setting. With a brand-new roof (2023), gutters, recently repainted interior and meticulously maintained grounds, this home is move-in ready and waiting for you to make it your own.
